step_data.thought:
I've successfully accessed the Orders Report page and set up the filter parameters to view sales orders for April 1, 2025. After clicking the 'Show Report' button, the report has been generated. Looking at the current page, I can see the report is displayed but it shows '0 records found' and the table says 'We couldn't find any records.' This indicates there are no sales orders for the specified date.

To provide a more useful analysis, I should try expanding the date range to capture more order data. I'll modify the date range to cover a longer period, for example, the past month. I'll update the 'From' date field to March 1, 2025, while keeping the 'To' date as April 1, 2025.
